# Reduce build context: build artifacts, env secrets, and largest dirs
.git
**/node_modules
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/target
**/venv
**/.venv
**/*.so
**/*.wasm
**/.eliza
**/.elizadb
**/*.log
**/.env
**/.env.*
.DS_Store
.github
.cursor
# Large dirs (keep all packages/ and plugins/ so workspace resolves)
examples
apps
eliza-cloud-v2
**/fonts
**/*.otf
**/*.ttf
**/*.woff2
